>        cgroup_post_fork(p);
>        return p;
>
> +bad_fork_free_graph:
> +       ftrace_graph_exit_task(p);
>  bad_fork_free_pid:
>        if (pid != &init_struct_pid)
>                free_pid(pid);
Very nice catch! Thanks.